Kar gamin kuuk Ruwwin ta Buŋdi beriy gay, ŋuur ko ele, galal, aapiy, subirraw, selliŋkaw, selliŋkaw, selliŋkaw, imaan,
Kar Iisa gay ƴalaaŋ di odinay a ŋaa tale waa kaak diiriiga.
Minninko-aŋ, ginno waan kaak gin ilim ho gin ilim dakina. Illa ŋaa gaare iŋ goyin̰ji kaak samaane ho iŋ dalullaw, kadar ŋa gin ilim. Illa ŋaa gaare iŋ riy taat ŋa gingiyo kadar ŋa gina gamin iŋ dalullaw.
Kar sultan kaawiiji ɗo gay riyor-ak aman: ‟ Ɗuunig asin̰ji iŋ pisin̰ji ho ɗuunoŋga, kar atkoŋ kara ɗo gondikor, ɗo wer kaak ŋu alaw ho ŋu eeyma saaŋco. "
Kar Iisa kaawiiji ɗo gem-ak aman: " Dak kaawenno bat ɗo waanna. Kar gay, ɓaa gaar zin̰ ɗo gay satkiner ho ber *satkin uudin taat gaanuun ka Muusa kaawtu. Paa kat, ŋuu ibine kadar ki cale "
Daarin̰co ɗiya aman: " Ŋa ŋaar ko Masi kaak Buŋ doɓtu. " Kar daarin̰ gay ɗiya aman: " Masi-ak yaa amile min Galile walla?
Min ŋa pakirtu pa-ak, ŋa ɓaawtu wer ka Mariyam atan̰ Yaaya kaak ŋu koliy oki Maark. Ɗo ger-ak, gee dakina n̰umtu ho ŋu salkiyaw.
Jeese roŋji ka Obeed, Obeed roŋji ka Booz, Booz roŋji ka Salmoon, Salmoon roŋji ka Nasoon.
Asaan zi kaak yaa zooɗe-ak yaa jipte iŋ kaak zooɗaaɗo. Ho zi kaak mataaɗo-ak yaa jipte iŋ kaak mate.
Kar ɗo wiktin taar-at, Iisa gay weƴa ka dariŋgildi. Maajirnay niiniig ho ŋu ɗiyiiji aman: " Gem kol tacco, ya ɗo botiliy-an, ki ginno tak-tak walla? "
Min ŋu obig Yaaya daŋaayne, Iisa uctu, ŋa ɓaawtu ɗo kiɗ ka Galile, ŋa gaariy Kabarre ta Gala taat asa min ɗo Buŋdi.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, gem kol siŋtay, oboŋ aditko samaane asaan nu aamin iŋ Buŋ ho nu iban kadar kaaw taat ŋa kaawiidu-an yaa ase uudin taat ka seener.
Asaan Buŋ, ŋaar Buŋɗo ka barjile, ŋaar Buŋ ka aapiyer. Ar kaak ɗo *Eglizna okin̰co ku gee ku Buŋdi,
Kar kuŋ gay iban kadar Iisa Masi as ɗo duniiner a ŋaa sooyin̰ zunuubinnite ku geemir. Zunuubinna, ŋuur ginno tak-tak.
Gee dakina minninco ɗiytu aman: " Ŋa gin aariɗ ho ŋa oliyo. Maa di ku cokiyiiga? "
Nu kaawaajiŋ a ki tiyaaɗo kum, ki saaɗo maam ku *bin̰di ho ki ginno maan kaak yaa iyin̰ siŋjiŋ yaa jage min botol ta Buŋdi.
Iisa gay telkiiji aman: " Ki ooy a kii ooye muutu ɗo bi kanto walla? Ka seener nu kaawaajiŋ, ka seener, kokir boogaaɗo di, kii tatire dees subba a ki ibinginno. "
Ɗo wer-ak di, mic-at uctu koɗok di ho ta teestu jaawe. Taar yaa nece ar elginay orok iŋ seer. Ɗo wer-ak, maajirnay ajbiytu tak-tak.
Gem kaak kaawa kaaw ɗo kaay ka meen̰ji di-ak, ŋa bariya ozile ka meen̰ji di. Kar ŋaar kaak bariya ozile ka ŋaar kaak tabirga-ak gay, ŋaar ka seener ho maan ginno ɗo gelbiney.
Iisa gay telkiico aman: " Maa di ku bariyiinu? Ku ibanno a illa naa goye ɗo ger ka Tanni walla? "
Nu taaƴiiciŋ-ak asaan wiktin taat nu ɓaa ɗo kiɗ ka Maseduwaan, nu taaƴiŋ-ak a kii goye ɗo geeger ka Epeez. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, kiico leese min gee daarin̰ kuuk ɓilda gee iŋ kaawin ku pey.
Kar ŋa kaawtu pey aman: " Di taloŋ, gee ku Israyeel okin̰co yaa ibine tak kadar Iisa kaak ku ɗooɗtu ka etor-aŋ, Buŋ ginig ŋaar-ak *Rabbine ho *Masi kaak ku ɗooɗtu. "
Simon Piyer iŋ *maajirin̰ce rakki ka pey aaɗiig Iisa. Maajirin̰ce-ak, mee satkiner ka tatko ibingiy dakina. Ampaa ko, ŋa un̰jitu iŋ Iisa ɗo wer ka berel ka ger ka mee satkiner-aka.
Dakoŋ moyenno ɗo bi ka teendi wala ka seendi. Dakoŋ moyenno ɗo gamin-aŋku,
Ɗo wer-ak, agindaw ku gaanuundi iŋ Pariziyenna dapin̰tu aale. Ŋu teestu kaawe benannico maan kaak ŋuu gine ɗo Iisa.
Hiyya, Iisa indiig paliinnay ku orok iŋ seera aman: " Kuŋko oki raka ɗeete walla? "
Iisa ɗiytu pey aman: " Ɗak mena sooɗ di, ku talaanno pey, kar ba aar sooɗ di, kuun talindu. "
Gem kol siŋtay, ya ku taaɓiya iŋ ay taaɓine, pakiroŋ kadar taaɓin-at yaa ase iŋ galal.
Iisa gay telkiico aman: " Nun aariɗɗo. Nu bera horoomine ɗo Tanni, kar kuŋ gay karmiyginu.
Iisa gay telkiico aman: " Gee kuuk cokiyit gaaƴ-an, ŋu bal kaawe ɗo bi kanto, kar gay, ŋu kaawiit ɗo bi kaŋko.
Ŋa osiite ampa-ak maman *ɗubil ka Buŋdi bayniiji ɗo geriy ho ŋa kaawiiji aman: ‟ N̰aam gee ɗo geeger ka Jappa, ŋu ɓaa kolin̰ Simon kaak ŋu koliy oki Piyer.
